{"tid":329212,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Dunkirk 集中討論區","createTime":"2017-07-20T07:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T08:17:26.000Z","uid":10113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7afe8d86abb0ff7809de4fdc720992881174b526","tid":329212,"uid":10113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/154842_d73d78918fb01f7beec6e4252a67dc87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F154842_d73d78918fb01f7beec6e4252a67dc87.jpg&h=8bf347d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我們毫不動搖，毫不氣餒。我們將戰鬥到底。我們將在法國作戰，我們將在海上和大洋中作戰，我們將具有愈來愈大的信心和愈來愈強的力量在空中作戰；我們將不惜任何代價保衛我們的島嶼。我們將在海灘上作戰；我們將在敵人登陸地點作戰；我們將在田野和街頭作戰；我們將在山區作戰；我們決不投降。我們在海外的帝國臣民仍要英國艦隊的武裝保護之下，繼續戰鬥，直到新世界在上帝認為適當的時候用它全部的力量和能力，來拯救和解放這個舊世界。」"},{"pid":"16c3dedb30ad80c327a621287c3c93ae06c4765c","tid":329212,"uid":10113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"啱啱IMAX睇完，好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n集合全部船隻，把士兵帶回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cd04f7e2e7995c8058adb8dbe7a1ae06c99a75","tid":329212,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/322312/page/6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/322312/page/6</a><br />\njm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5048fdad33119bc2256724217df2446e03d3578","tid":329212,"uid":10113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"屌，睇唔到添"}]}